PrecisConfirmation of the request made to the Hon. ROGER C. SIMMONS, P.C., M.P., to travel to Reykjavic, Iceland, from Oct. 20th to Oct. 26th, 1990, as an official Canadian representative accompanying a delegation of citizens from Gaultois, Newfoundland, in their search for potential operators for the Gaultois Fish plant.
